Return

$OUVRE
If clalev([F:AXXM])=0 : Local File ATEXTRA      [AXXM] : Endif
If clalev([F:AXXP])=0 : Local File ATEXTRA      [AXXP] : Endif
If clalev([F:AXXC])=0 : Local File ATEXTRA      [AXXC] : Endif
