& Char     A_TABJ1(20),
& Char     A_TABJ2(15),
& Char     A_TABJ3(80)
& ) From Variable A_BUFJ1, A_BUFJ2, A_BUFJ3
& As [PCEJ]
Return

$TIT_JOIN
